---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Hakkımızda">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Image -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160399-112ba8d25d1d?q=80&w=2000&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Background" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/90"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center">
        <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-red-100 text-accent rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
          Hakkımızda
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
          SY Sağlık Ürünleri
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          1992'den bu yana sağlık sektöründe güvenilir, yenilikçi ve yüksek kaliteli çözümler sunuyoruz.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Us Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Biz Kimiz?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            SY Sağlık Ürünleri Şirketi, sağlık sektöründe güvenilir, yenilikçi ve yüksek kaliteli çözümler
            sunma hedefiyle <strong class="text-gray-800">1992 yılında</strong> kurulmuştur.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            <strong class="text-gray-800">Kardiyoloji, radyoloji, nöroloji, anestezi, üroloji, kalp ve damar cerrahisi, diyaliz ve genel cerrahi</strong> alanlarında; tek kullanımlık balon, stent, kateter ve guide wire gibi medikal ürünlerin tedarik ve satışını gerçekleştiriyoruz.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Hasta güvenliğini ve tedavi başarısını ön planda tutan yaklaşımımızla, sağlık profesyonellerine etkin, güvenilir ve sürdürülebilir çözümler sunuyoruz.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Teknolojiyi yakından takip eden, etik değerlere bağlı, kalite odaklı bir anlayışla; ülkemizde ve uluslararası pazarlarda sağlık sektörüne değer katmayı sürdürüyoruz.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-accent/5 rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
              <div class="flex items-center space-x-4 mb-6">
                <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-white font-serif font-bold text-2xl">SY</span>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl">SY Sağlık Ürünleri</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-500">1992'den beri hizmetinizde</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Kardiyoloji & Radyoloji</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Nöroloji & Anestezi</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Üroloji & Diyaliz</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                  </svg>
                  <span class="text-gray-700">Kalp Damar Cerrahisi & Genel Cerrahi</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision & Mission -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold mb-4">Vizyonumuz</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            İnsan sağlığını merkezine alan, yenilikçi ve güvenilir ürünlerle Türkiye'de ve dünyada medikal sektörün öncü markalarından biri olmak.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Kalite, teknoloji ve etik değerlere dayalı hizmet anlayışımızla, sağlık profesyonellerinin ilk tercihi haline gelmeyi hedefliyoruz.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-semibold mb-4">Misyonumuz</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">SY Sağlık Ürünleri Şirketi olarak;</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Tek kullanımlık medikal ürünlerde yüksek kalite ve güvenilirliği ön planda tutmak</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Etkin ve yenilikçi çözümler sunmak</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Hasta güvenliği ve tedavi başarısını esas almak</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Sağlık hizmetlerinin sürdürülebilir gelişimine katkı sağlamak</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="section-title">Değerlerimiz</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle mx-auto">
          İş yapış şeklimizi belirleyen temel değerlerimiz
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6">
        <!-- Value 1: Güven -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Güven</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Hasta ve hekim güvenliğini en öncelikli değer kabul ederiz.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2: Kalite -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Kalite</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Uluslararası standartlarda ürün ve hizmet sunarız.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3: Yenilik -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Yenilik</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Sağlık teknolojilerini takip eder, yeniliği merkezimize koyarız.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 4: Etik -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Etik</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Dürüstlük, şeffaflık ve etik sorumluluk ilkelerine bağlıyız.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 5: İşbirliği -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">İşbirliği</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Sağlık profesyonelleriyle güçlü ortaklıklar kurarız.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 6: Sorumluluk -->
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 12a9 9 0 01-9 9m9-9a9 9 0 00-9-9m9 9H3m9 9a9 9 0 01-9-9m9 9c1.657 0 3-4.03 3-9s-1.343-9-3-9m0 18c-1.657 0-3-4.03-3-9s1.343-9 3-9m-9 9a9 9 0 019-9"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Sorumluluk</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Topluma, çevreye ve paydaşlarımıza karşı sorumluyuz.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quality Policy -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-accent rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="section-title">Kalite Politikamız</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">
            SY Sağlık Ürünleri Şirketi olarak, müşterilerimize sunduğumuz her ürün ve hizmette:
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Ulusal ve uluslararası kalite standartlarına tam uyum sağlamayı</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Sürekli iyileştirme ve müşteri memnuniyetini temel almayı</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Çalışanlarımızın bilgi, beceri ve sorumluluk bilincini sürekli geliştirmeyi</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Etik, güvenli ve sürdürülebilir iş süreçleri yürütmeyi</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start space-x-4">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Sağlık sektöründe uzun vadeli güven ilişkileri oluşturmayı</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          
          <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-100">
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-center italic">
              "Amacımız, kaliteyi yalnızca bir hedef değil, kurumsal kültürün vazgeçilmez bir değeri haline getirmektir."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
